Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ドキドキハラハラ こんなのはじめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまで私の 気持ちをもてあそぶの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,無視無視ムリムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,突然始まる 大スペクタクル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっと言わせる為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてを 賭けてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每日 大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,お気楽マイペース男の子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,とぼけた顔してもダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,だけど つい見ちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:38.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のこと 気になって！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今度は何にするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}緊張兮兮 神經兮兮 從來沒試過這種感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你要玩弄人家的感情到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}無視無視 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}突然開始的大奇觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}動員自己的一切腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}就是為了讓我大喊一聲「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每天都搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你這個不安分又特立獨行的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一臉無辜的表情也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}絕對在搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不過又忍不住看過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}好在意 你這次又搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說要表達什麼做什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用to加動詞的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫做不定詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種用法…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君又在玩將棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前才玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣的東西就不會吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能專心聽課了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼步兵一個人對其他所有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,530)\shad0\bord0\c&H1F2123&}第8節課 將棋②
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼亂來的將棋沒法玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個步兵到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公 公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將棋裏根本沒那種棋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擅自亂造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵和公主在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王和全軍是兩人的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說這狀況是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外國電影裏經常演的那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一介士兵與公主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後對此怒不可赦的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與所有人為敵的愛情大逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等浪漫的將棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一手都要好好關注啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哄而上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵都遍體鱗傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣絕對贏不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步→夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主→婦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫婦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無比絕望的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人結下了不可動搖的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公好強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛的力量讓夫變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣 憑著那股氣勢把礙事的都幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 公主被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣要怎麼戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要在公主眼前將他慢慢折磨致死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經堅持不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是剛才被打飛的敵人金將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這裏面還有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是那個夫的父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被洗腦了派去跟兒子戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子危機之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復神智的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕來救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是正常的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用課本當牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 要怎樣才能跨越這道堅固的門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕快的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下一頁 關你來念一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要念課本就得拿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在意想不到時候得到貴人相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天助我也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君是不會得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開了 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那防禦工事是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是在課本的背後做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才短短時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是人肉城牆是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父子的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道從哪裏開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35頁 關君35頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課小動作

